OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780016591
OL,3,C300,000 new work placements pledged
OL,4,C'to help young people build lasting
OL,5,Ccareers'
OL,7,FTens of thousands of new work
OL,8,Fexperience and training placements
OL,9,Ffrom construction to hospitality will
OL,10,Fbe available for young people as part
OL,11,Fof Government efforts to tackle the
OL,12,Fjoblessness crisis.
OL,14,FThe 300,000 new placements over the
OL,15,Fnext three years are backed by some of
OL,16,FBritain's biggest employers, Work and
OL,17,FPensions Secretary Pat McFadden said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
