FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780016591
OL,3,C300,000 new work placements pledged
OL,4,C'to help young people build lasting
OL,5,Ccareers'
OL,7,FThese include Manchester and Gatwick
OL,8,Fairports, and the Government has vowed
OL,9,Fplacements will reach young people
OL,10,Facross the country.
OL,12,FThe placements, also expected to
OL,13,Finclude health and social care, have
OL,14,Fbeen confirmed just a day after a
OL,15,Freport warning of the risk of a "lost
OL,16,Fgeneration".
OL,26,@wD@aOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
