OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780016591
OL,3,C300,000 new work placements pledged
OL,4,C'to help young people build lasting
OL,5,Ccareers'
OL,7,FThe number of the UK's 16 to 24-year-
OL,8,Folds not in employment, education or
OL,9,Ftraining ` known as Neets ` rose to
OL,10,Fmore than a million, figures published
OL,11,Fon Thursday confirmed.
OL,13,FFormer Labour cabinet minister Alan
OL,14,FMilburn, who was tasked with leading
OL,15,Fthe review into Neets, wrote that lack
OL,16,Fof work experience is "the single most-
OL,17,Fcited barrier to work amongst young
OL,18,Fpeople".
OL,26,@xD@WOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780016591
OL,3,C300,000 new work placements pledged
OL,4,C'to help young people build lasting
OL,5,Ccareers'
OL,7,FHis report said: "At present, the
OL,8,Fprovision of work experience is an
OL,9,Fafterthought for many schools.
OL,10,FStudents are often told to find their
OL,11,Fown placements. Unsurprisingly, those
OL,12,Fwithout strong networks and
OL,13,Fconnections are more likely to miss
OL,14,Fout."
OL,16,FThe review author said the "first rung
OL,17,Fof the career ladder has thinned" and
OL,18,Fis now "simply out of reach" for many
OL,19,Fyoung people.
OL,26,@oD@ROUvD@EO]xD@\OUyD@aO]zD@HOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780016591
OL,3,C300,000 new work placements pledged
OL,4,C'to help young people build lasting
OL,5,Ccareers'
OL,7,FHe added: "That places them in a
OL,8,Fhopeless Catch-22 where employers ask
OL,9,Ffor work experience but the
OL,10,Fopportunities for young people to gain
OL,11,Fit have narrowed or gone."
OL,13,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,14,Fsaid the 300,000 placements will
OL,15,Fcomprise of work experience and what
OL,16,Fare known as Sector-based Work Academy
OL,17,FProgrammes (Swaps).
OL,26,@oD@KOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
