FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780016591
OL,3,C300,000 new work placements pledged
OL,4,C'to help young people build lasting
OL,5,Ccareers'
OL,7,FThe latter are short Government-funded
OL,8,Fprogrammes for jobseekers claiming
OL,9,Fbenefits, offering training, hands-on
OL,10,Fexperience of the workplace and a
OL,11,Fguaranteed job interview, the
OL,12,Fdepartment said.
OL,14,FMr McFadden said: "The evidence is
OL,15,Fclear, give young people real work
OL,16,Fexperience and the chances of them
OL,17,Fbuilding a lasting career increase
OL,18,Fdramatically.
OL,26,@vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
