CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780016591
OL,3,C300,000 new work placements pledged
OL,4,C'to help young people build lasting
OL,5,Ccareers'
OL,7,F"That's why we are creating 300,000
OL,8,Fnew placements, backed by some of
OL,9,FBritain's biggest employers, to give
OL,10,Fyoung people the skills, confidence
OL,11,Fand connections they need to get on.
OL,13,F"This generation deserves every
OL,14,Fopportunity to succeed, and this
OL,15,FGovernment is determined to deliver
OL,16,Fit."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@DO]
